metadata.description:
Each Abstract Pepl is inspired from artworks from Crypto Punks, Cool Cats, CyberKongz, Murakami.Flowers, BAYC, Azuki and Doodles.

 This Pepl used Murakami.Flower #1714 as inspiration: https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0x7d8820fa92eb1584636f4f5b8515b5476b75171a/1714 

 You and I are Pepls. We're adding the colors back to the market.
